larification.\u201d Source: al-Bah\u0323r\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/22\/ibn-al-mubarak-leave-anger\/","url_meta":{"origin":21509,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Mubarak on Akhlaq: Good character is to abandon anger","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 22, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: It was said to Ibn al-Mubarak, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cSummarize good character for us in a single sentence.\u201d Ibn al-Mubarak said, \u201cLeave aside anger.\u201d Ibn Rajab said, \u201cThe same explanation was offered by Imam Ahmad and Ishaq ibn Rahawayh, that good character is to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24507,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/10\/ahmad-akhlaq-sabr-anger\/","url_meta":{"origin":21509,"position":2},"title":"Ahmad on Akhlaq: Good character is patience, restraining anger","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 10, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: Imam Ahmad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cGood character is to not get angry or enraged. Good character is to patiently endure what comes from people.\u201d Source: J\u0101mi' al-'Ul\u016bm wal-\u1e24ikam 1\/457 #18 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0631\u062c\u0628 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0625\u0650